2014-02-27 00:18:16	technomancy	smrtz|nix: tmk firmware lets you do that
2014-02-27 00:18:26	technomancy	you can have up to 32 layers
2014-02-27 00:18:30	smrtz|nix	technomancy: oh?  how?
2014-02-27 00:18:39	technomancy	magic =D
