2014-02-27 14:28:55	eckse	smrtz|nix: two things you should know
2014-02-27 14:29:17	eckse	one: wasd is pretty much the only company that offers custom caps
2014-02-27 14:29:25	smrtz|nix	Damn.
2014-02-27 14:29:31	eckse	*customized sets
2014-02-27 14:29:51	smrtz|nix	Yeah, that's exactly what I'm looking for.
2014-02-27 14:30:00	eckse	you can buy keycaps from signature plastics, but I'm not sure about their lettered keycaps
2014-02-27 14:30:07	eckse	two: wasd keycaps are shite
2014-02-27 14:30:14	smrtz|nix	really?
2014-02-27 14:30:16	eckse	yes
2014-02-27 14:30:18	eckse	all around
2014-02-27 14:30:20	eckse	crap
